  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">On 4th November 2020 conflict between several factions and government military erupted, shelling and gunfire ensued. Warring fighters took what they needed leaving the most vulnerable without crops, livestock and / or earning power. For many their communities were destroyed, others lost their lives and have fled their homes. One million internally displaced people in Shire, Abraham&apos;s Oasis is feeding 1000. 200 unaccompanied minors are to come under our protection until life is stable for them.</narrative>
  </description>
